description:
We promised, you delivered! We got a bunch of folks registered with Headcount.org and as promised, our Pokémon themed West Wing-inspired political thriller one-shot. Enjoy, and for those of you in the United States, go vote on Tuesday!


Enjoyed the game? Check it out! It's called Executive Decision by Greg Stolze


Editing by Chad Ellis


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
